latestIgtvVideos.title: Don’t Matter💙 (From a girl’s perspective)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sharing a little backstory for this one: 

I’ve always loved @akon’s music, his vibe, his style & of course his voice and lyrics. I heard don’t matter for the first time when I was in the 5th grade and I took it up as a personal challenge to master the rap! It was so fun to see everyone’s reaction when a 10 year old girl sang that rap with all the swag😛🙆🏻‍♀️
I also landed up changing the lyrics from a girls perspective👧🏻🥰 (watch till the end for that) 

If you enjoy it, please do LIKE, COMMENT, SAVE & SHARE as your story!✨

latestPosts.caption:
Sharing a piece of my heart with you all♥️
‘𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐀𝐫𝐞 𝐀 𝐂𝐫𝐢𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐚𝐥’ is yours now✨

—

‘𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐀𝐫𝐞 𝐀 𝐂𝐫𝐢𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐚𝐥’ is an Orchestral Pop song. It’s not only my 10th original song but also my 1st record label release under Salim-Sulaiman Sir’s Merchant Records. To be able to release a song that I’ve written, composed and sung under their label is a feeling I can’t seem to put into words. ‘𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐀𝐫𝐞 𝐀 𝐂𝐫𝐢𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐚𝐥’ is one big metaphor with a different take on heartbreak, the heartbroken and the heartbreaker aka the criminal. It takes you on a journey through heartbreak and betrayal.

Also available on Instagram music! Use it on your stories and make some lit reels! Re-sharing the best ones on my story🤩
